### Attempt 1
To install pandas version 1.3.5 from the official Python Package Index (PyPI), you can use the following command in your terminal or command prompt:

```bash
pip install pandas==1.3.5
```

This command will download and install the specified version of pandas, which is compatible with the dataset 'https://raw.githubusercontent.com/datasciencemasters/uci-ml-datasets/master/winequality-white.csv'.